title: Omae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai (You Don't Know Gunma Yet)
synopsis: Nori Kamitsuki has recently moved to the Gunma prefecture from Chiba, following after Otoya Todoroki, a former friend who moved there in elementary school. While on the way there, he receives an ominous text message from Todoroki telling him to turn back and that once someone enters Gunma, they never return.
